{"tid":2078574,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和你論壇·初選為咗乜【新界西】6月25日下午5時-7時","createTime":"2020-06-25T06:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T17:36:04.000Z","uid":145118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb2fd007339e0da584627eb5e07e0508ff60e6d","tid":2078574,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T06:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xWUjzMt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxWUjzMt.jpg&h=087ea549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▉和你論壇 &middot; 初選為咗乜 <br />\n新界西： 朱凱迪 、黃子悅 、張可森 、伍健偉 、岑敖暉<br />\n-<br />\n📍地點：荃灣廣場空地（AEON對面）<br />\n📆時間：2020年6月25日端午節下午5時至7時<br />\n📢主持：荃灣區議員陳劍琴<br />\n🙂講者：民主派初選參選人<br />\n── 張可森、黃子悅、伍健偉、岑敖暉、朱凱廸<br />\n-<br />\n//這幾天落區擺設街站的時候，總會有市民問及什麼是民主派初選，亦有人質疑這是一場「小圈子選舉」。我們幾個民主派初選參選人將在論壇現身說法，解釋初選的重要性以及香港人如何面對國安法危局。<br />\n<br />\n誠邀大家抽空，一人幾分鐘，好好和你論壇。//<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKLegCo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKLegCo&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=23b97544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKLegCo</a><br />\n<br />\n*民主派初選非為民主派搞，實為一班選民發起，李伯盧為最初起發人，勿將民主派與民主派初選混淆，多一份信念多一份力量！唔係有希望先去堅持，係有堅持先有希望！謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39e64b695b70ad267d15e3604ce9597b6efc89d","tid":2078574,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yKwU4l4QKUU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyKwU4l4QKUU&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=c398019a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yKwU4l4QKUU</a>"},{"pid":"9d9601eb23731a46bf1fb8dca605386ad730f9da","tid":2078574,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VvqKLXj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/