67d1b8d996652e9ad313baa80","tid":2078574,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asCxavB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasCxavB.jpg&h=966a0cfa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01de1a36c0c2fed6c8025eedf823248f340bbb4a","tid":2078574,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KDwq32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KDwq32.jpg&h=f5ee76f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分裂問題今時今日仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be261f8de0fd1837a1ea27cf031304c917d16628","tid":2078574,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DELiQvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDELiQvV.jpg&h=f5df112e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4508e5716a2731dbeb94f9fd38418ea0eb04e8d","tid":2078574,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSNJha1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSNJha1.jpg&h=db290b65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f5237c0c70bd3a3be14f918b7b0097d7d440c5d","tid":2078574,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3BucKD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3BucKD.jpg&h=a8298c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勿麻木</span></span>"},{"pid":"68ddcd019b4a70b037df1c20528cc1ddee75a369","tid":2078574,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:28:05.000Z","msg":"#手足家書 #手足支援 #齊上齊落 #和你寫<br />\n<br />\n謊言重覆千遍，就能蹂躪人確實存在的記憶，將虛妄之言變成「真實」。<br />\n<br />\n中共的「洗腦」好比毒瓦斯，沉浸多了亦不知中毒太深。懇請香港人記得，要將真實資訊，帶給身陷囹圄的每一個人 &mdash; 不管是肉身的牢籠或是思想的監獄。要光復香港，「智」、「勇」不可缺一。讓我們以智慧，粉碎中共的謊言，以勇氣，揭示暴政的荒謬，集和勇之力瓦解極權。<br />\n<br />\n收藏家家書全文: ✍🏼✍🏼✍🏼<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/手足收藏家家書-06-23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2F%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%E6%94%B6%E8%97%8F%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%B6%E6%9B%B8-06-23&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=29f65f97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegra.ph/手足收藏家家書-06-23</a><br />\n<br />\n牆內時間難耗，願各位能寄信及書本給在囚手足，讓關懷和資訊化為黑獄中的彩虹🌈。以下為相關活動：<br />\n<br />\n1. 和你寫信/和你做筆友：<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0%E5%AF%AB-02-23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2F%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%25AF%25AB-02-23&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=ac64e4e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegra.ph/%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0%E5%AF%AB-02-23</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 《和你讀》(撰寫不同類型文章供牆內手足閱讀)：<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/14048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F14048&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=20391e2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/14048</a><br />\n<br />\n**手足收藏家希望收到牆外書信，並交托邵家臻議辦作中轉站，大家可參考「和你做筆友」的做法，並在信封列明「收藏家」名字。🤗<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n🔈民間記者會現有官方帳號：<br />\n<br />\nOfficial webpage: <a href=\"http://www.citizenspc.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=3d1c75fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.citizenspc.org</a><br />\nTG channel: <a href=\"http://t.me/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=b137b739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/citizenspresscon</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://fb.me/hkercpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Fhkercpc&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=704ffbd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.me/hkercpc</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=3b64a56a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/citizenspresscon</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2OVdv6T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OVdv6T&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=d210f083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2OVdv6T</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/citizenspc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2Fcitizenspc&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=3f00d4b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.twitter.com/citizenspc</a>"},{"pid":"a8f01ad94d54515a44f2f74026b81aba83aec978","tid":2078574,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"【緊急急急～分享轉發保選票平安】麻煩大家用1分鐘時間，喺6月25日申索及反對期前查核自己所登記嘅選民資料。<br />\n檢查選民資格： <a href=\"http://tinyurl.com/checkmyballot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fcheckmyballot&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=d59a91cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tinyurl.com/checkmyballot</a><br />\n⠀⠀<br />\n正常情況下，大家係會有2票可以投：⠀<br />\n1）地方選區 （如新界東、九龍西、離島等）⠀<br />\n2）區議會（二） （亦稱「超級區議會」）⠀或其他功能組別<br />\n3）如果你係團體負責人而又有其他功能組別成功登記<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你check完發覺有問題，例如喺登記冊搵唔到自己名、少咗票、資料錯誤等等，可以於辦公時間內致電 2891 1001 向選舉事務處查詢～⠀<br />\n⠀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />提出申索（appeal）表格下載：<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/appeal.htm⠀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fappeal.htm%E2%A0%80&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=7558ab2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/appeal.htm⠀</a><br />\n可於6月25日09:00-18:00 遞交表格至香港灣仔港灣道二十五號海港中心十樓／九龍九龍灣展貿徑一號九龍灣國際展貿中心十三樓的辦公室⠀<br />\n⠀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />截止日期（今日）為公眾假期，為免查詢／申請有所延誤，請盡快盡快盡快check清楚！( ･᷄ὢ･᷅ )⠀<br />\n⠀<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nFollow以下channel以獲得立法會選舉資訊<br />\nTG：2020立法會選舉資訊轉運站<a href=\"https://t.me/legco20mansuen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flegco20mansuen&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=1f0b0478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/legco20mansuen</a><br />\nIG：legco20takeitall<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6970c675c012a4fe8a49b45764393ce1fc72e3fe","tid":2078574,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"[全民反國安 - G20國聯署請願行動]<br />\n<br />\n國安法草案即將落實，預計有可能於下月實施。屆時，香港將失去獨立司法制度，對香港的人權及自由，本土營商、勞工環境以及各國的利益均會做成重大損害，而本港作為國際城巿的地位亦岌岌可危。<br />\n<br />\n為顯示香港人民反國安法，維護人權及公義的決心，主辦單位將聯同區議員及其他本土組織收集聯署，並向G20國集團及台灣領事館/辦事處進行馬拉松式請願，尋求國際社會的支持，阻止中共破壞一國兩制，人權及香港司法獨立地位，維持獨立營商環境，及保障各國在港僑民福祉及商人的在港利益。<br />\n<br />\n以下為向G20國集團及台灣領事館/辦事處聯署信內容:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c%2Fedit&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=76f64de7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n網上聯署 (2020年6月25日2359前):<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfc3FrAKQ9C0VVAftfvjvLtAP32_qF31kkoeJNXCBfvfl1kpA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfc3FrAKQ9C0VVAftfvjvLtAP32_qF31kkoeJNXCBfvfl1kpA%2Fviewform&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=9d34ff17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfc3FrAKQ9C0VVAftfvjvLtAP32_qF31kkoeJNXCBfvfl1kpA/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n實體聯署表格 (請列印並邀請身邊的人簽署, 並於6月25(四)交往以下街站 (沙田小巴站, 1400-1700; 旺角  旺東橋 moko 入口, 1100-1700; 或朗豪坊雅蘭對出, 1400-1900):<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/10bIZEDuFWiVibPR8vRCk4AtuyCwisPf3/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F10bIZEDuFWiVibPR8vRCk4AtuyCwisPf3%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=ca585352\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/10bIZEDuFWiVibPR8vRCk4AtuyCwisPf3/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n國安法實施後，港人將面對中共的白色恐怖，言論、結社、新聞自由等基本人權將不復存在。主辦單位懇請各位港人把握機會，合力爭取。<br />\n<br />\n全民反國安，還我真香港！香港人，反抗！<br />\n<br />\n主辦 :<br />\n香港會計手足工會<br />\n香港金融業職工總會<br />\n政府非公務員職工總會<br />\n香港貿易推銷及採購職工會<br />\n香港旅遊業革新總工會<br />\n香港資訊科技界工會<br />\n香港寵物界工會<br />\n社會及政治組織從業員工會<br />\n香港調酒師工會<br />\n香港幼兒教育工作者工會<br />\n香港設計師工會<br />\n<br />\n［行動post ］［請置頂］G20國請願！簽名師召喚！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2077187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2077187</a><br />\n<br />\nFB Post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGeneralStrike9293/posts/290804232294947?__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKGeneralStrike9293%2Fposts%2F29080